val zee_json_valid = sqlContext.sql(s"""select id, metadata from zee_json where statusCode = 200""")
zee_json_valid.createOrReplaceTempView("zee_json_valid")

val zee_json_valid_stp1 = sqlContext.sql(s"""select id,
from_json(metadata, 'title String').title AS title,
from_json(metadata, 'season String').season AS season,
from_json(metadata, 'tvshow String').tvshow AS tvshow,
from_json(metadata, 'tvshow_details String').tvshow_details AS tvshow_details,
from_json(metadata, 'episode_number String').episode_number AS episode_number,
from_json(metadata, 'duration String').duration AS duration,
from_json(metadata, 'asset_subtype String').asset_subtype AS asset_subtype,
from_json(metadata, 'genre String').genre AS genre,
from_json(metadata, 'description String').description AS description
from zee_json_valid""")
zee_json_valid_stp1.createOrReplaceTempView("zee_json_valid_stp1")

val cms = sqlContext.sql(s""" select 
id as tms_id,
from_json(genre, 'value String').value AS genre_list,
asset_subtype AS category_type,
title AS episode_name,
description,
from_json(tvshow_details, 'cover_image String').cover_image AS cover_image,
from_json(tvshow_details, 'image_url String').image_url AS image_url,
duration AS content_length,
from_json(season, 'index String').index AS season_number,
from_json(tvshow, 'title String').title AS series_name,
episode_number,
from_json(tvshow_details, 'actors String').actors AS actors
from zee_json_valid_stp1""")

cms.createOrReplaceTempView("cms")

%sql select 
sum(if (tms_id is null or tms_id = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as tms_id_coverage,
sum(if (genre_list is null or genre_list = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as genre_list_coverage,
sum(if (category_type is null or category_type = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as category_type_coverage,
sum(if (episode_name is null or episode_name = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as episode_name_coverage,
sum(if (description is null or description = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as description_coverage,
sum(if (content_length <= 0 or content_length is null or content_length = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) content_length_coverage,
sum(if (season_number = 0 or season_number is null or season_number = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) season_number_coverage,
sum(if (series_name is null or series_name = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as series_name_coverage,
sum(if (episode_number = 0 or episode_number is null or episode_number = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) episode_number_coverage,
sum(if (actors is null or actors = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as actors_coverage,
sum(if (cover_image is null or cover_image = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as cover_image_coverage,
sum(if (image_url is null or image_url = '', 0, 1)) / sum(1) as image_url_coverage
from cms
